high_descs: Go to the right side of the table and face it where the tomato and ladle is.
Pick the ladle up from the table.
Go left and walk to the sink and face it.
Put the ladle in the sink and turn the water on, turn the water off, pick the ladle up.
Move to the right and face the cabinet below, and to the right of the sink.
Open the lower cabinet to the right of the sink, put the spoon in and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed ladle on a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right, go straight, turn left, go straight, then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the spoon, on the table in front of the egg.
Turn left, go straight then turn left, then turn right to go to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Turn around, then move forward, then turn back around to face the cabinets beneath the sink.
Place the spoon in the cabinet on the right, on top of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon in the cabinet.

high_descs: move toward the right hand side of the white round table and face the table
pick up the spoon from the table
turn to the left move forward a few steps, turn left, move forward and turn right moving towards the sink
put the spoon into the sink and turn on the water to clean the spoon, turn off the water and pick up the clean spoon
turn to the lower cabinet that is to the right of the sink
open the cabinet door, put the spoon into the cabinet in front of the sponge and close the cabinet door
anns.task_desc: put a clean spoon into the cabinet
